âœ… BASIC TEMPLATE
p1 = head1
p2 = head2

while p1 != p2:
    p1 = p1.next if p1 else head2
    p2 = p2.next if p2 else head1

return p1

ğŸ§  ONE-LINE MEMORY (PUT IN GITHUB README)
Two Pointer Linked List:

1) Speed diff â†’ middle, cycle
2) Distance diff â†’ from end problems
3) Meet/compare â†’ palindrome, intersection

ğŸ§  SUPER SHORT DECISION RULE (EXAM)

Ask only one question:

â“ Does problem mention END / LAST?
â¡ use distance pattern

â“ Does it mention MIDDLE / CYCLE?
â¡ use speed pattern

â“ Does it mention MATCH / PALINDROME?
